Vector Machines (SVM) algorithm. In fact, each egg has been
assigned to the most matched clutch. An egg classification
accuracy of 53% has been reached.
Furthermore, in [15] a proposed method to identify the
parasitic cuckoo egg from the Great Reed Warbler (GRW)
and Eurasian Reed Warbler (RW) based on visual features
of egg. The aim of this study is to detect the parasitic egg of
