Analysis of Learning Behavior Characteristics and
Prediction of Learning Effect for Improving
College Students’ Information Literacy
Based on Machine Learning
YONG SHI
1, FANG SUN2, HONGKUN ZUO3, AND FEI PENG1
1School of Computer Science, Huainan Normal University, Huainan 232038, China
2Institute of Education, Huainan Normal University, Huainan 232038, China
